BOARD OF EDUCATION OF THE TOWN OF KIEFER, Oklahoma, et al. v. BROWN-CRUMMER INVESTMENT COMPANY. No. 267. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit, April 5, 1930. Redmond S. Cole, of Tulsa, Okl., for appellant. Val jean Biddison, of Tulsa, Okl., for appellee.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed April 5, 1930, per stipulation.
